          "_name": "pricing04",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"pricing04 startm5\" group=\"Pricing\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButton\" title=\"Buttons\" checked>\n    <header>Card</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showText\" title=\"Text\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showList\" title=\"List\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButtons\" title=\"Buttons\" checked>\n    <header>Color</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" name=\"cardsHead\" title=\"Head\" value=\"#5bc12f\">\n    <input type=\"color\" name=\"cardsBg\" title=\"BG\" value=\"#f7f7f7\">\n    <input type=\"color\" name=\"iconColor\" title=\"Icon Color\" value=\"#9fe870\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\">\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-lg-4\">\n        <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12\">\n          <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\"><b>Soluciones en Hardware &amp; Software</b></h5>\n          <h6 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle, .main-button\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">Ofrecemos soluciones completas en hardware y software, desde el diseño electrónico hasta el desarrollo de firmware. <br><br>Elige el plan que mejor se adapte a tu proyecto y hagámoslo realidad juntos.</h6>\n         <div class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3 main-button\" mbr-if=\"showButton\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/593995546906\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Contáctanos</a></div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"col-lg-8 side-features\">\n        \n        <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 item-mb active\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"item-head\">\n              <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Plan Colaborativo</b></h5>\n              <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\"><b>DESDE $25/hora</b></h6>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Pensado para startups, emprendedores<br>que buscan crecer con apoyo tecnológico.<br></p>\n              <div class=\"mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showList && showText\">\n                </div>\n              <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-if=\"showList\">\n                <ul>\n                  <li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Consultoría inicial</b><br></li><li><b>Diseño de hardware</b></li><li><b>Diseño de Software</b></li><li>\n</li><li><b>Desarrollo de firmware\n</b></li><li><b>Desarrollo de prototipo</b></li><li><b>Soporte técnico.</b></li>\n                </ul>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer \" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/593995546906\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">CONTRATAR</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 item-mb\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"item-head\">\n              <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Desarrollo de Producto</b></h5>\n              <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n                <b>DESDE $3200/mensual</b></h6>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Dirigido a empresas e industria<br>que requieren soluciones exclusivas.<br><br></p>\n              <div class=\"mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showList && showText\">\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-if=\"showList\">\n                <ul>\n                  <li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Consultoría especializada</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Diseño de hardware</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Desarrollo de firmware</b></li><li><b>Diseño de Software&nbsp;</b><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">(web, escritorio, APIs)</b></li>\n                  <li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Desarrollo de prototipo</b><br></li><li><b>Documentación completa (BOM, planos, manuales, pruebas)</b></li><li><b>Derechos 100% del cliente (propiedad intelectual incluida)</b></li><li><b>Soporte técnico.</b></li>\n                </ul>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer \" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/593995546906\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">CONTRATAR</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 item-mb\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"item-head\">\n              <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Desarrollo de Hardware</b></h5>\n              <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n                <b>DESDE $1300/mensual</b></h6>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Clientes que ya cuentan con su propio equipo de software/firmware y necesitan únicamente diseño electrónico profesional.<br><br></p>\n              <div class=\"mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showList && showText\">\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-if=\"showList\">\n                <ul>\n                  <li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Consultoría especializada</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Esquemático y PCB.</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Optimización de diseños existentes.</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Gerbers, BOM, Pick&amp;Place.</b></li><li><b>Gestión de prototipos.</b></li><li><b>Revisión mecánica y documentación.</b></li>\n                </ul>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer \" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/593995546906\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">CONTRATAR</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 item-mb\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"item-head\">\n              <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Desarrollo de Firmware</b></h5>\n              <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n                <b>DESDE $950/mensual</b></h6>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Equipos que ya tienen hardware pero necesitan programación para habilitar todas las funciones del dispositivo.<br><br><br></p>\n              <div class=\"mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showList && showText\">\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-if=\"showList\">\n                <ul>\n                  <li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Consultoría especializada</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Firmware en C/C++ , python o MicroPython.</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Drivers, protocolos y conectividad.</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">OPTA, OTA, WiFi, BLE, LoRa, MQTT</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Pruebas y depuración en hardware real.</b></li>\n                </ul>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer \" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/593995546906\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">CONTRATAR</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-6 item-mb\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <div class=\"item-head\">\n              <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Desarrollo de Software</b></h5>\n              <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n                <b>DESDE $1700/mensual</b></h6>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item-content\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Clientes que necesitan aplicaciones o sistemas independientes, aun cuando no tengan hardware. Ideal para empresas o equipos que requieren herramientas digitales, automatización o plataformas web para su negocio.<br><br></p>\n              <div class=\"mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showList && showText\">\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"counter-container mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article mbr-if=\"showList\">\n                <ul>\n                  <li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Consultoría especializada</b></li><li><b style=\"font-size: calc(1.07rem + 0.13 * ((100vw - 62rem) / 25));\">Desarrollo de aplicaciones web independientes.</b></li><li><b>Dashboards y paneles administrativos.</b></li><li><b>Sistemas internos para gestión o automatización.</b></li><li><b>APIs y servicios backend.</b></li><li><b>Integración con bases de datos y plataformas en la nube.</b></li><li><b>Herramientas de monitoreo y control digital.</b></li>\n                </ul>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer \" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><a href=\"https://wa.me/593995546906\" class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">CONTRATAR</a></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
